# Thai Visa Company Internal Linking Standard

Every blog article strengthens the editorial knowledge graph. Links must help readers â€” never insert links solely for SEO.

**Canonical reference:** [`docs/editorial-knowledge-graph.md`](../../docs/editorial-knowledge-graph.md)  
**Frozen graph:** [`lib/content/editorial-knowledge-graph.ts`](../../lib/content/editorial-knowledge-graph.ts)  
