## Publication terminology

| Use | Do not use (our content) |
|-----|--------------------------|
| blog article | guide, authority guide |
| visa page | visa guide |
| Related articles / Keep reading | related guides |
| Read article | Read guide |

## Each blog article must

- link to the relevant **visa page** for requirements
- link to related **blog articles** when the reader has a fork question
- link upstream to **best-visa-for-living-in-thailand** when route selection is unclear
- receive links from visa hubs via `relatedArticleSlugs` when cluster-primary
- use frozen `relatedSlugs` from the knowledge graph (3â€“4 max)

Manual `related` + `relatedSlugs` beat algorithmic links in `lib/content/related.ts`.

