## Visa hub backlinks

Each `/visas/*` hub must list `best-visa-for-living-in-thailand` plus cluster-primary articles (see knowledge graph doc Â§3).

## Anti-patterns

| Anti-pattern | Why |
|--------------|-----|
| Hub fee/checklist tables in comparison articles | Visa pages own requirements |
| Linking `/visas/tourist` from DTV vs tourist | Tourist pillar unpublished |
| `elite-worth-it` â†” `elite-vs-retirement` in every section | Hierarchy: worth-it â†’ vs-retirement â†’ hubs |
| Duplicating re-entry rules on every hub | `re-entry-permit-thailand` owns compliance |
| Hub â†” hub loops in blog body | Service navigation belongs on visa pages |

